ing Glass (  1872 ), who was based on his child friend  Alice Liddell , daughter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Alice Rockhill was born in 1100, in Arkesden, Essex, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of GODfrey Rockhill. She married Mr Rockhill about 1119, in Arkesden, Essex, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1100–":"1100–Surnud","1100–Female":"1100–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1120–1194":"1120–1194","1070–Male":"1070–Surnud","Between 1120 and 1130":"1120 kuni 1130","1100":"1100","1120":"1120","1194":"1194","Abt 1119":"umbes 1119","1070":"1070","Of, Wygpet, Arkesden, Essex, Eng":"Arkesden, Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Wygpet, Arkesden, Essex, England":"Arkesden, Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Lavington, Wiltshire, England":"Lavington, Wiltshire, England"},"fi":{"1100–":"1100–Kuollut","1100–Female":"1100–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1120–1194":"1120–1194","1070–Male":"1070–Kuollut","Between 1120 and 1130":"vuodesta 1120 vuoteen 1130","1100":"1100","1120":"1120","1194":"1194","Abt 1119":"noin 1119","1070":"1070","Of, Wygpet, Arkesden, Essex, Eng":"Arkesden, Essex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Wygpet, Arkesden, Essex, England":"Arkesden, Essex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Lavington, Wiltshire, England":"Lavington, Wiltshire, England"},"fr":{"1100–":"1100–Décédée","1100–Female":"1100–Décédée","–Male":"Décédé","1120–1194":"1120–1194","1070–Male":"1070–Décédé","Between 1120 and 1130":"du 1120 au 1130","1100":"1100","1120":"1120","1194":"1194","Abt 1119":"environ 1119","1070":"1070","Of, Wygpet, Arkesden, Essex, Eng":"Arkesden, Essex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Wygpet, Arkesden, Essex, England":"Arkesden, Essex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Lavington, Wiltshire, England":"Lavington, Wiltshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Alice 